column9: where are you building at fr?
check the buildings for passenger levels  .. that iron and coal mine have passengers too
or... you can build a bus network in a city to fill your train with passengers & mail
Yes but i'm starting with a little city: Sheffield
just remember that passengers have a specific destination just like factories (so you gotta connect a lot of houses)
oh, and you may not want to make your train stations public; they can never be deleted once they are public... so it's risky to make too many public stations
that car assembly plant needs lots of passengers
